<item>
            <title>[LU-491] conf-sanity/50g fails on a local setup</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-491</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;conf-sanity/50g fail on a local setup because wait_osc_import_state() in t-f finds two imports:&lt;br/&gt;
osc.lustre-OST0001-osc-MDT0000.ost_server_uuid=lustre-OST0001_UUID	FULL&lt;br/&gt;
osc.lustre-OST0001-osc-d973213c.ost_server_uuid=lustre-OST0001_UUID	FULL&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;and doesn&apos;t parse this correctly&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;orion is affected as well&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>local setup (all the services run on a single node)</environment>
